# support chinese font file

We need to hack source code to use ttc font file.
The source file is MATPLOTLIB_PACKAGE_ROOT/font_manager.py;
change

```
'ttf': ('ttf', 'otf')
```

to

```
'ttf': ('ttf', 'ttc', 'otf')
```

Then clean the cache in ~/.cache/matplotlib, and reload package